<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٢١٣٥ - ر ع ف]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>رعِفَ يَرعَف، رَعَفًا، فهو راعِف<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• رعِف الشَّخصُ:</span> رعَف؛ سال الدَّمُ من أنفِه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>